re Notes</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2016-06-14T16:36:43.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"qinwf/awesome-R","categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Packages</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/jalapic/engsoccerdata\">engsoccerdata</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/jalapic/engsoccerdata\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">626</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":626,\"repo\":\"jalapic/engsoccerdata\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - English and European soccer results 1871-2016.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-06-14T15:45:18.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"deephacks/awesome-jvm","categoryHTML":"<h2>Memory and concurrency</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/OpenHFT/Zero-Allocation-Hashing\">Zero-Allocation-Hashing</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/OpenHFT/Zero-Allocation-Hashing\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">571</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":571,\"repo\":\"OpenHFT/Zero-Allocation-Hashing\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Hashing a